\ LP format - for model browsing. Use MPS format to capture full model detail.
\ Signature: 0x7cd2115bd4d1e070
Maximize
  x_0
Subject To
 R0: x_0 >= 1
 R1: x_0 <= 1
 R2: alpha_0 <= 1
 R3: - alpha_0 <= 1
 R4: alpha_1 <= 1
 R5: - alpha_1 <= 1
 R6: 0.25 alpha_0 - 0.5 alpha_1 <= 1.75
Bounds
 x_0 free
 alpha_0 free
 alpha_1 free
End
